        <updateDate>2020-11-02T12:52:33Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>End Taxpayer Subsidies for Drug Ads Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits tax deductions for expenses relating to direct-to-consumer advertising of prescription drugs. </p> <p><i>Direct-to-consumer advertising</i> is any dissemination, by or on behalf of a sponsor of a prescription drug product, of an advertisement that is (1) in regard to the drug product, and (2) primarily targeted to the general public. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
